We are excited to launch our brand-new website! 😊 The Chinese Canadian Association of Kingston and District has been serving our community since 1977, and this redesigned site makes it easier than ever to stay connected.

**What's new:**

- New [member's portal](https://members.ccakd.ca) to let you see your membership status, payment history, and pay members fee online!
- Browse upcoming events and register online
- View photo galleries from past community gatherings
- Learn about our programs and activities
- Read announcements in English, Simplified Chinese, and Traditional Chinese

We welcome your feedback as we continue to improve. Please reach out to us at [info@ccakd.ca](mailto:info@ccakd.ca) with any suggestions.
